!colspan="5" style="font-size:85%;"|Source: Office for National Statistics<ref name="2001urbanarea" /><ref name="2001ethnicdata">{{Citation |url=http://www.statistics.gov.uk/statbase/ssdataset.asp?vlnk=8283&More=Y |title=KS06 Ethnic Group: Census 2001, Key Statistics for urban areas |publisher=National Statistics |accessdate=2009-02-16}}</ref><ref name="2001agestructure">{{Citation |url=http://www.statistics.gov.uk/statbase/ssdataset.asp?vlnk=8272&More=Y |title=KS02 Age Structure: Census 2001, Key Statistics for urban areas |publisher=National Statistics |accessdate=2009-02-16}}</ref><ref name="2001religiondata" />
